_sText:
Use this map for surfing, so put [sv_airaccelerate 100] in console.

There two main routes at the start, one for good surfers and one for goos shooters. Then there is a large arena with the opportunity to go to the pro tower which has AWPs and a route to go turn on lasers in Mini Arena. 

Enjoy, Atreides.

ENJOY DAMN YOU!!!!!
